Note: ─── Import System in EPL ───
Note: This file demonstrates importing code from other files

Note: Import a utility file (path relative to where you run EPL from)
Import "examples/math_utils.epl"

Note: Use the imported function
Print add(3, 4)
Print multiply(5, 6)

Note: Use the imported constant
Print PI

Note: Use in calculations
radius = 5
area = PI * (radius raised to 2)
Print area
